External libs
-------------

# plotutils
+++++++++++++
> ./configure
> make

maby error by compile: replace

setjmp(png_ptr->jmpbuf)        -> setjmp(png_jmpbuf(png_ptr))
longjmp (png_ptr->jmpbuf, 1);  -> longjmp(png_jmpbuf(png_ptr), 1);

- put in LD_LIBRARY_PATH the location where the libplot.so is
- be sure the "graph" executable is in your "PATH"

# silo
+++++++++
> ./configure
> make

# jansson
++++++++++
> ./configure
> make

by linking meschach_ef demos , error -> Replace in jansson.h "real" with "xreal"


# spooles
++++++++++
> make lib
> cp spooles.a libspooles.a

> cd LinSol
> make lib
> cp Bridge.a libBridge.a

# vogle/vopl
+++++++++++++
build in the project (modified)

# pgplot
+++++++++
just compile ?

follow the instructions 
- g77 must be on system
- rename untar'ed folder "pgplot_srcs"
- create new "pgplot" folder and copy in it the file "drivers.list"
- cd in your "pgplot" folder
- drivers.list: select PPM, GIF, XWINDOW, XSERVE, XADRIV(ATHENA) - not Motif!
- ../pgplot_srcs/makemake ../pgplot_srcs  linux g77_gcc

# lua
+++++++++
just compile
> make



env variables (linux) :

export MESCHACH_EF=$HOME/GITHUB/meschach_ef
export PGPLOT_DIR=$MESCHACH_EF/EXTERNAL_LIBS/pgplot
export PGPLOT_DEV=/XWINDOW

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:$MESCHACH_EF/EXTERNAL_LIBS/plotutils-2.6/libplot/.libs

export VDEVICE=X11
export VFONTLIB=/usr/local/lib/hershey or /usr/share/hershey-fonts  # copy all fonts of vogle in this folder
export P6TO=PPM
